Offline Go module cache
=======================

This directory contains pre-downloaded Go module archives used for
offline/airgapped builds when the Go module proxy is unavailable.

Contents:
  go-sqlite3-v1.14.22.zip  — github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3 v1.14.22

Usage (manual build without network):

  mkdir -p $(go env GOMODCACHE)/cache/download/github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3/@v
  cp vendor-cache/go-sqlite3-v1.14.22.zip \
     $(go env GOMODCACHE)/cache/download/github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3/@v/v1.14.22.zip
  GOFLAGS=-mod=mod GONOSUMCHECK=github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3 go build ./cmd/server

Or use GOPROXY=file:// to point Go at a local module mirror.
